        "subject": "LU-9667 lnet: Userspace control to show lnd connections",
        "message": "LU-9667 lnet: Userspace control to show lnd connections\n\nAdding build_lnd_conn_tree() function to show\nlnd connections for each lnd peer with\n\"lnetctl peer show\" command.\n\nAdding helper functions in liblnetconfig.c to show lnd\nconnections and its statistics for each lnd peer along\nwith lnet peer information.\n\nChange-Id: I3026a496ae8df9c524aa263f872e3f9b55279e12\nTest-Parameters: trivial\nSigned-off-by: Sonia Sharma <sonia.sharma@intel.com>\n"
